g.text: Source: CREA based on AirVisual, Oxford COVID-19 Government Response Tracker

text.style: font-size: 8.80px; font-style: italic; fill: #35416C; font-family: Arial;

g.text: The line represents the PM2.5 anomaly i.e. the difference between observed an predicted PM2.5 level based on previous years air quality and weather data (2017-2019). It is smoothed using a 30-day running average., MODIS and HYSPLIT.

text.style: font-size: 8.80px; font-style: italic; fill: #35416C; font-family: Arial;

g.text: Lockdown is defined as periods when people are required not to leave house (1: recommended; 2: curfew; 3: total confinement).

g.text: Fire activity refers to the sum of fire radiative power along air trajectories leading to each city.
